CHAPTER 101 - COMPROMISE
However, the order badge in Ye Xuan's hand, was not fake, because he also had one, but the material was slightly worse than the one in his hand.
Right now, there were only two possibilities. Firstly, Ye Xuan had accidentally obtained the order badge, and secondly, Ye Xuan really knew Ouyang Ming.
"City Lord Zhang, please give me the token." Ye Xuan suddenly reminded.
Zhang Lie threw the token back. He had no idea what he should do now.
"Mayor Zhang, I wonder if you can release him now?" Ye Xuan looked at Zhang Lie with a smile that was not a smile.
"No way!" Zhang Lie shouted subconsciously.
Ye Xuan slightly nodded his head, and laughed: "Since City Lord Zhang does not believe, then I can only go to the Southern Cyanwood Forest City to find Master Ouyang. At that time, I believe Master Ouyang will thoroughly investigate who is the traitor
and want to sell out the country.
After he finished speaking, he turned around and left. His speed was extremely fast and exceeded everyone's reactions.
"This is bad!"
Zhang Lie's face instantly sank, he did not expect Ye Xuan to leave so quickly, and gave him no time to hesitate, he immediately shouted: "Wait!"
By the time his voice sounded, Ye Xuan had already appeared tens of meters away.
If Zhang Lie's shout was a little slower, he might have flashed out of the others' line of sight. He faintly smiled, turned around and said, "City Lord Zhang, is there anything else?"
Zhang Lie looked at him gloomily and said slowly, "Cao Ba, let them go!"
Compromise, compromise!
Everyone present was shocked. The City Lord of Thousand Gold City, who always kept his word, actually compromised with Ye Xuan.
However, when they thought about the Ouyang manor's command medallion in Ye Xuan's hands, they calmed down as well.
If Ye Xuan really knew Inspector Ouyang Ming, then Zhang Lie would be dead for sure. He would give the Xue Family the crime of colluding with the enemy and selling their country.
He didn't dare to gamble, so he compromised!
Not long after, Cao Ba walked out with a group of Xue Clan members. These days, the Xue Clan members had been locked up in fear. Who would have thought that they would see the light of day again one day.
"Ye Xuan, is that you?"
When Xue Hai saw Ye Xuan, he also suddenly realized something. Speaking of which, his Xue Family did not know many people, so other than Ye Xuan, who else could have saved the Xue Family?
"Uncle, take a look. Have all the captives arrived?" Ye Xuan said as he looked at Xue Hai.
Xue Hai looked around, then nodded and said, "We're here. All the prisoners are here."
Ye Xuan also looked around, there were about 30-40 people here, but he did not see anyone.
"Uncle, where's Master Lian?" Ye Xuan suddenly remembered that day, the former lecturer from the Falling Cloud Sect who helped the Xue Family lie him.
Upon hearing this name, Xue Hai's brows tightly knitted. He said, "Master Lian, you've been beaten to death."
"Alright, I understand!"
This news also made Ye Xuan's heart jump, although he had only met Lian Yuan once, he had at least helped him once.
In order to take revenge on him, Zhang Lie had not only captured all the members of the Xue Clan, but had also killed them. If that was the case, he would have to pay the price of blood.
However, this was not the time to make a move!
At this time, Ye Xuan suddenly turned around and said: "City Master Zhang, since you copied the Xue Family, other than releasing the people, do you want to compensate for the losses you incurred?"
"Ye Xuan, don't go too far!" Zhang Lie immediately reprimanded.
The reason why he had compromised by letting go of Xue Zhen and the others was because these people no longer had much to use.
When he was plundering the house, he had already taken away all the valuable things of the Xue Clan, even all the assets of the Xue Clan.
It was impossible for him to return these items and to compensate for his losses!
One had to know that this was an astronomical figure.
"Hehe, good. Let's not talk about this for now. The portrait of my fiancee, Xue Qingqing, is still stuck at the city gate. Isn't it time for the mayor to put down the wanted poster?" Ye Xuan looked at Zhang Lie.
"Hmph." Zhang Lie harrumphed coldly and instructed a person to head to the city gate and take down the wanted poster.
"Alright, then City Lord Zhang, we'll meet again next time!"
After Ye Xuan revealed a devilish smile towards Zhang Lie, he hurriedly left with Xue Hai and the others, and then arrived at the inn where Xue Qingqing was hiding.
"Father!"
After Xue Qingqing saw Xue Hai, she also flew over. She suddenly discovered that Xue Hai's body became a lot skinnier, and even his white hair grew quite a bit.
"Ye Xuan, it's all thanks to you this time, if not, we would have been dead for sure." Xue Hai said with tears streaming down his face.
"Uncle, this matter started because of me. It was I who harmed you." However, you all will not be able to stay in this Thousand Gold City for much longer. Ye Xuan suggested.
"That's right. We have already broken off all relations with Zhang Lie and we can only leave. Even Cloud City is a good place to go. Although I don't have any money now, I, Xue Hai, believe that I will definitely rise again."
Although Xue Hai felt very regretful in his heart, all the assets of the Xue Family had been taken over by Zhang Lie. They had no money and Lian Yun City was a small city.
"Uncle, since that's the case, let's head out now."
As Ye Xuan spoke, he immediately left and bought a few horse carriages, preparing to escort Xue Hai and the others to Lianyun City.
Now that the Xue Clan had been expropriated and was unable to pay the salary for those offerings, they had all left. Some had even joined the Zhang Clan.
That afternoon, Ye Xuan brought the Xue Family's team to Lianyun City.
The convoy did not have a single guard, but with Ye Xuan present, they would be fine.
On the way to Lianyun City, Ye Xuan used the excuse of cultivation to stay in a carriage and instructed others not to disturb his cultivation.
However, in the evening, he took advantage of the fact that no one was paying attention to him and quietly left.
His goal was to return to Thousand Gold City!
You are not a gentleman if you do not seek revenge!
Zhang Lie plundered the Xue Family, and even killed the company elder who had helped Ye Xuan before. Therefore, when Ye Xuan returned this time, he wanted Zhang Lie to pay the price, the price of blood!
Of course, before he left, he had already secretly told his plan to Guan Lan.
With Guan Lan here, the convoy would be relatively safe.
The caravan was not fast, although they had walked for half a day, but with Ye Xuan's physique, it did not take him long to return to Thousand Gold City.
Right now, Xue Qingqing's wanted poster had already been removed, so there were fewer guards at the city gate as well, saving the need for searches. Ye Xuan put on a bit of disguise before sneaking into the city.
At this moment, it was already night.
"The Xue family has just left and the City Lord's Mansion has been destroyed. The people will definitely suspect me. However, I don't care about all that.
On a certain rooftop, Ye Xuan who was dressed in black looked at the lights of the Thousand Gold City's City Lord's Mansion and revealed a weird smile.
https://largepdf.com/
CHAPTER 102 - CITY LORD'S MANSION, ANNIHILATED!
Tonight was destined to not be a peaceful night!
No one noticed that a black shadow had already flashed into the City Governor's Estate.
At this time, in a certain room in the City Lord's Mansion, there were two figures. One was the Thousand Gold City's Zhi Lie, and the other was the Cao Ba who was beaten up by Ye Xuan earlier in the day.
Zhang Lie sat on a chair, his expression extremely gloomy. His brows were tightly knitted, as if he was pondering over some problem.
"City Governor, you're letting them leave just like that?" Standing in front of Zhang Lie, Cao Ba asked.
"I also didn't expect that kid to actually know the Imperial Investigator. It looks like I'm quite good with that kid." However, I didn't expect the Xue Clan to be so rich, with more assets than I, the City Lord, this is not bad. In addition, now that the Xue Clan
has left Thousand Gold City, from now on, Thousand Gold City is my, Zhang Lie's, world.
"Congratulations City Governor!"
Cao Ba hurriedly cupped his fist and said.
Although he had been sent flying by Ye Xuan and suffered some injuries, he heard even more that Fan Yue had been crippled by Ye Xuan. Someone as bold as him was not someone he could afford to offend.
One had to know that there were many people who wanted to avenge Fan Yue. Besides the Sky Cracking Sect, there was also the Fan family from the Southern Cyanwood Forest!
Just as Zhang Lie and Cao Ba were discussing how to develop the Thousand Gold City in the future, a shadow suddenly rushed in from outside the door.
"Reporting to City Lord, someone has invaded!"
"It isn't just one or two people that have ideas on my City Lord's Mansion, and you still want to report to me?" Zhang Lie frowned and said.
The guard who came to report swallowed his saliva and stammered, "City Lord, this time it's an expert. We've been killed by him!"
"What?"
Cao Ba exclaimed, wondering if he had misheard.
Each squad of guards in the City Lord's Mansion had ten people, and they were all at least at the sixth stage of the Martial Dao.
"Looks like this person is at least at the eighth stage of Martial Dao. City Lord, I'll be right back!" Cao Ba left with a cold expression.
After all, those who died were his subordinates.
Zhang Lie did not mind. After all, right now he was the sole ruler of his clan. He would definitely be coveted by quite a few people.
Cao Ba was one of his trusted aides whom he had recruited with great difficulty. He believed that with Cao Ba's strength, he would definitely be able to capture that thief and deliver him to him.
But this time, he was wrong, and ridiculously wrong.
"Strange, Cao Ba has already left for more than ten minutes. Could it be that with his abilities, he is still unable to deal with that intruder?" Zhang Lie's heart was filled with astonishment. Just as he was about to personally go out and take a look, he was
shocked to discover that someone had ambushed him.
"You dare to sneak attack me, you're truly overestimating yourself!"
Zhang Lie dodged the attack. However, the next moment, he was shocked to discover that what he dodged was not a concealed weapon, nor a bow, but a head.
Furthermore, he recognized this head. It was actually the head guard of the City Lord's Mansion, Cao Ba!
"What?"
Zhang Lie panicked, Cao Ba was at the ninth stage of the Martial Dao, the same as him. However, Cao Ba's head was already chopped off, so the opponent must have had the ability to kill him.
"Who dares to be so impudent in my City Lord's Mansion?" Although Zhang Lie had some fear, he was the city lord of a city and an official of the Mysterious Sun Empire. Not everyone would have the guts to kill him.
"City Lord Zhang, how have you been?"
Suddenly, a female voice rang out, and a black figure landed within his courtyard.
"A woman?"
Zhang Lie quickly thought about it. However, he could not recall anything. He did not recognize this voice.
This man in black was actually Ye Xuan. Before sneaking into the City Lord's Mansion, he had used a bit of his devouring points to buy a Soundchanging Pearl inside the Devouring System to disguise as a mature woman's voice. In addition, he had also
disguised himself as a black-clothed person and the night sky.
"City Lord Zhang is really forgetful. It seems that you have already forgotten what you did to my family. Today, I have come for revenge!"
Ye Xuan purposely spoke very loudly, allowing the people around him to hear his words.
"That year?"
Zhang Lie's face darkened. He had done too many things before. He couldn't recall which family's child this tall woman before him was from.
"Cut the crap. Zhang Lie, today is the day you die!"
Ye Xuan shouted as he rushed in front of Zhang Lie. Using his gloved right hand, he punched Zhang Lie in the chest.
"Bam!"
After receiving such a heavy blow to his heart, Zhang Lie's heart stopped.
Ye Xuan was at the middle stage of the ninth stage of the Martial Dao, a realm higher than Zhang Lie. In addition to the Hundred Beast Bloodline and high level martial arts, he could easily kill Zhang Lie in an instant!
"Run! The mayor is dead!"
Immediately, all the guards outside dispersed with a bang. Even Zhang Lie and Cao Ba, who were at the ninth stage of the Martial Dao, were dead. What were they still doing here?
Ye Xuan who had killed Zhang Lie secretly revealed a smile.
"Fuse with the blood of the Treasure Seeking Deer!"
Ye Xuan said in his heart.
Treasure Seeking Deer bloodline was also a low level bloodline, but its value was 300 points, three times that of the Hundred Beast Bloodline.
Treasure Seeking Deer, as its name implied, was specifically used to search for treasures. After fusing with this bloodline, one could sense things that contained spirit energy in a certain area, such as medicinal herbs, Dan s, etc.
It was also because of this that Ye Xuan did not keep Zhang Lie alive.
"Ding! Fusion successful!"
The system's notification rang in his head.
"Alright, let's start looking for the good stuff!"
After fusing with the blood of the Treasure Seeking Deer, Ye Xuan could obviously feel that there were good things around him, only, he didn't know where they were.
The blood of the Treasure Seeking Deer could only be sensed, that's why it was so cheap.
"It seems to be in Zhang Lie's study."
Ye Xuan glanced at his surroundings, and then strode into the study room.
The study room was not big, but there were a few bookshelves inside, and Ye Xuan immediately felt that something was amiss.
There was something fishy going on!
He checked and soon found a mechanism.
"Crack!"
The two rows of bookshelves suddenly moved away, revealing a passage that led underground.
"It's just a little trick, it's not difficult at all." Ye Xuan snorted, then started to walk down.
Before he could go all the way, he encountered several special iron gates. However, these iron gates could at most stop the Warrior of the eighth stage, but for Ye Xuan, it was not difficult at all.
After a while, Ye Xuan looked at the pile of Treasure Chests in front of him, and could not hold back his laughter.
This was probably the Zhang Clan's treasury. Perhaps, there was something inside that had been looted from the Xue Clan.
"Forget it, let's just put them in the Devouring Space to talk!"
Ye Xuan ignored everything and kept all these things in the Devouring Space.
Although he didn't know whether or not these items were Zhang Lie's entire possessions, he knew that the City Lord's Mansion would definitely have many other treasures.
Since he had come, he might as well earn enough!
https://largepdf.com/
CHAPTER 103 - BREAKTHROUGH
As the City Lord, Zhang Lie Gui was definitely extremely wealthy. Furthermore, there were many ministers in the Zhang Residence, and all of them were taken care of by Ye Xuan.
In this city, no one could stop Ye Xuan, who was like a vampire sucking blood frantically.
Not only that, he also found some assets of the Zhang Family, including those of the Xue Family. After leaving the City Lord's Mansion, he had visited all of these shops, including the Dan s, weapon stores, and House of Kung Fu Knowledge s.
"Awesome, awe-inspiring! Awesome! Just the amount of banknotes I received already amounted to 200 million!"
After robbing the last restaurant, Ye Xuan could not help but shout in his heart.
Just the silver alone was worth two hundred million. If you added in the loot, the income this time was at least five hundred million, and that was not even including the treasury under the Mayor's mansion. Including the treasury, it was at least seven to
eight hundred million.
Because something had happened to the City Lord's Mansion, the city walls had been closed ahead of time. However, even the special door to the treasury below the City Lord's Mansion could not stop Ye Xuan, much less these ordinary city gates.
"Not good, the killer who killed the mayor has fled the city!"
The guard shouted.
Today, the Thousand Gold City was destined to fall into chaos.
With the death of the City Lord, the entire City Lord's Mansion had been looted. Not only that, the properties under the City Lord's Mansion were also looted.
However, Ye Xuan was not worried at all. He was afraid that the higher ups would only think that an expert robbed the City Lord's Mansion for money.
During the chaos in Thousand Gold City, Ye Xuan had already rushed to the Xue Family's convoy at full speed.
"Huff huff, no one noticed." Ye Xuan returned to his carriage and quickly changed his clothes.
This time, his harvest would be the biggest ever. He was prepared to leave those silver with the Xue Clan and those martial arts.
As for everything else, it was completely absorbed!
"Ding! Host has broken through to the peak of the ninth stage of Martial Dao!"
After the journey through the Eighteen Lian Cloud Mountain Range, Ye Xuan had reached a point where he was on the verge of a breakthrough. After devouring so many things, Ye Xuan had directly broken through to the peak of the ninth stage of the
Martial Dao, just one step away from the tenth stage.
"Damn it, the amount is getting bigger and bigger. Once I reach the tenth stage of the Martial Dao, the amount of things I'll need will probably go up to a billion."
Ye Xuan felt a headache coming on, but he had a plan to earn money the entire time, it was just that he didn't have a place to implement it.
"Buy an Intermediate Bloodline and play."
Right now, Ye Xuan was a nouveau riche with a total of 1500 points of Devour. However, to raise his Blood of the Wind Chaser Leopard to Intermediate, it would only need 1000 points to do so.
But in the next moment, Ye Xuan was stunned.
"The host is currently unable to fuse with an intermediate level bloodline. If you try to forcibly integrate it, it might cause your cultivation level to drop or your body to explode. Do you want to purchase it?"
The system prompted.
"What?" Unable to fuse them? " Ye Xuan was startled.
It seemed that it was because his cultivation wasn't high enough?
Helpless, he could only choose to give up and wait for the tenth stage of the Martial Dao to finish.
At this moment, the sound of footsteps came from outside the carriage, immediately followed by an elegant voice, "Ye Xuan, are you there?"
It was the voice of a loli. It was very obvious that it was Xue Qingqing who had come, not Guan Lan.
"Didn't this girl say not to look for me?" Ye Xuan rolled his eyes. He had clearly said before that he would not disturb his' cultivation '. Luckily he came back early, otherwise, wouldn't he be exposed?
"Come in."
Ye Xuan said. The next moment, he saw a petite figure slip in.
However, the interior of the carriage was extremely dim, and she could only vaguely make out the location where Ye Xuan was sitting.
"Why are you looking for me?" Ye Xuan asked.
"You are my fianc, I must find you for something?" Xue Qingqing said with some dissatisfaction.
"Yes, of course." Ye Xuan laughed, the reason he had so many of them was just to not let others know that he had gone out. Now that he was back, he naturally did not care.
"It's all thanks to you this time. Otherwise, in a few days, the mayor would have already beheaded my family." Xue Qingqing said gratefully.
"You said it earlier, I'm your fianc. If I don't help you, who will?" Ye Xuan said.
"Alright, then I won't be unreasonable." Xue Qingqing smiled knowingly and continued, "Is that sister your senior sister?"
Ye Xuan nodded, "I guess so."
He knew that Xue Qingqing was definitely referring to Guan Lan, but it didn't matter whether Guan Lan was his Junior Sister or Senior Sister.
In terms of age, Guan Lan was older than him, but in terms of strength, he was far stronger than Guan Lan.
"Hmph, it's only been a short while since I've entered the Cloud Cracking Sect and I've met such a beautiful senior sister. Didn't I say not to attract bees and butterflies?" Xue Qingqing wrinkled her nose, her face filled with dissatisfaction.
"I didn't." Ye Xuan rolled his eyes, he did not want to get involved, but since Guan Lan was sticking close to him, what could he do?
However, in the next moment, he was also stunned.
"Hmph, I'll forgive you this time. There can't be a next time." Xue Qingqing suddenly said in a compromising manner.
"Holy shit, is this the default permission " Ye Xuan was a little helpless.
Just then, the carriage's curtain was pulled open again, and a white figure entered. It was Guan Lan.
When Guan Lan saw Xue Qingqing entering the carriage, she knew that Ye Xuan had returned. She carefully sized him up, and only heaved a sigh of relief after ensuring that he wasn't injured.
However, what made Ye Xuan even more helpless was that the two girls actually started to chat, and the more they chatted, the more excited they became, completely taking Ye Xuan to the side.
As for the silver wolf cub, he quietly laid beside Ye Xuan and similarly revealed a helpless expression.
.
Since they were traveling by carriage, the speed of the Xue Clan's convoy wasn't fast. It took them about a week before they arrived at Lianyun City.
Immediately, Ye Xuan brought them to the Ye Family household and contacted the Lin Family to convene the conference.
Even though Lian Yun City is only a small city, the three great families are confident that they can develop it into a big city. As long as they can reach a certain level of prosperity, they can become a big city and at that time, they can appoint a city lord.
Ye Xuan also returned the two hundred million silver back to the Xue Clan. Although the Xue Clan's property was gone, Xue Hai was a merchant, and he knew more people. As long as there was money, starting a new business would not be a problem.
Ye Xuan did not take out the martial arts and techniques of the Cracking Cloud Sect. After all, he had some principles. As for the martial arts techniques, he took them out and imprinted a few of them before sending them to the three great families.
It was almost the new year, so Ye Xuan was not in a rush to return to the Falling Cloud Sect, since Guan Lan had nothing to do, he agreed to stay at the Ye Family to celebrate the new year with Ye Xuan.
The New Year celebration in this world was not too different from the one on Earth. Everyone had a family dinner together.
https://largepdf.com/
CHAPTER 104 - UNFRIENDLY PERSONS
It was the same for large families like the Ye family, but there were also a lot of them. Whether they were surnamed Ye or surnamed Ye, they all had a banquet at the training field.
However, on this joyous day, something big suddenly happened to the Ye Family.
Suddenly, someone broke into the Ye Family mansion, and after killing a few guards, he suddenly died.
When Ye Zhang heard about this, he hastily led his men over. However, when he clearly saw the corpse, his face turned pale.
He then anxiously returned to the training grounds and called Ye Xuan over.
Ye Xuan originally did not know about this, but after seeing the corpse, he was completely shocked.
This was because this person was actually wearing the robes of the Cracking Cloud Sect, and it was even the attire of the Elder.
"Who is it?" Ye Xuan turned the Elder over in surprise, and then exclaimed: "Elder Lu?"
The person who suddenly broke into the Ye Family and started a massacre was Lu Kui's grandfather, the Road Pool Road's Elder.
Ye Xuan immediately understood the sequence of events.
"That day when we went down to the Black Water Lake together, maybe some bandit saw us and heard about it from the road pool, but I lied about it before, so he thought that Lu Kuang's death was related to me and came to take revenge. But, how did he
die?"
Ye Xuan began to investigate the cause of death. When he took off Lu Elder's clothes, he was shocked to find out that Lu Elder's entire left chest had caved in.
"Elder Lu is at the middle of the tenth stage of the Martial Dao. I'm afraid that whoever can kill him with a single punch would be at the peak of the tenth stage of the Martial Dao, but "

He had already condensed his Dan Yuan, so when it came to dealing with ordinary peak of the True Profound Realm, he could defeat them as easily as Ye Xuan.
"Next!"
Ye Xuan's voice once again sounded throughout the entire competition grounds.
At this time, nearly a hundred individuals had already gathered in the battlestage. There were disciples of the Earth Province, as well as those from the Black Yellow Mansion that had come to try their luck.
When they heard these words, they couldn't help but be startled as well.
Ye Xuan had only challenged a Strongman at the peak of the True Profound Realm, and now he was challenging someone who was half a step into the Dan Yuan Realm?
One had to know that even if the low rank Spirit Level Martial Art was used using Dan Yuan, its power would still be much stronger than the middle rank Spirit Level Martial Art.
If he were to use the high-grade Spirit Level Martial Art, its power would be comparable to an Earth Realm martial art.
"Go up and cripple him!" Tang Tian's face darkened once again as he said softly.
"Yes sir!"
The cold-looking teenager nodded in agreement before he slowly walked towards the arena.
Everyone's eyes fell on him.
Tang Yaoguang, ranked nineteenth on the Earth Rankings, half a step into the Danyuan stage.
This person's realm had already surpassed everyone present. It was just that they didn't know who was stronger between Ye Xuan and him.
Although Ye Xuan had won so many matches in a row, he was going to face a half step into the Danyuan stage, a half step into the pericelestial stage.
Sone Caijing looked at Tang Yaoguang, his brows tightly knitted together. She whispered to Ye Xuan who was standing on the stage: "Enough, you have already avenged yourself, stop challenging.
Ye Xuan turned his head and laughed: "Since this is revenge, then we cannot give up halfway."
"No, you can't beat him. Get down here." Sone Caijing said anxiously.
"I can even send someone at the peak of the True Profound Realm flying with a punch. What, you don't believe it? Why don't we bet once more, on what happened before? " Ye Xuan asked.
"No, come down quickly." Sone Caijing glanced at it, and realized that Huang Yaoguang was already at the bottom of the stage, walking up the stage, and immediately felt a shiver in his heart.
"If you don't want to bet, then I won't." Ye Xuan shamelessly shrugged his shoulders.
Sone Caijing compromise said: "Alright, then it's my loss, hurry up and get down."
"Aren't you just not trusting my strength? Just wait and see." Ye Xuan replied calmly.
Even though he and Sone Caijing were enemies before, they were only doing it during the assessment. After interacting with Sone Caijing for a while, he realized that they were still quite cute little girls.
Just now, Tang Tian's actions had caused him to be misunderstood by Sone Caijing, which made Sone Caijing cry even more.
When Ye Xuan saw Sone Caijing's moist eyes, he had already made his decision.
He had to avenge this enmity!
It was precisely because of this that he chose to break through and cause the Great Tang Empire to lose face.
Let him go down?
Impossible!
At this time, Huang Yaoguang had already walked up the stage, causing Sone Caijing to jump up anxiously as well, ready to pull Ye Xuan off the stage.
"It's enough that you've promised so many matches. You don't have to risk your life for this. Although there will not be any casualties in this stage, Tang Tian is obviously going to cripple you, you don't need to " Sone Caijing pulled Ye Xuan's arm, and
said softly.
